        "creation_date": 1400440451,
        "body": "<p>You most likely got inproper <code>AndroidManifest.xml<\/code> file, with no Activity registerd for<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>    &lt;intent-filter&gt;\n            &lt;action android:name=\"android.intent.action.MAIN\" /&gt;\n            &lt;category android:name=\"android.intent.category.LAUNCHER\" /&gt;\n        &lt;/intent-filter&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>I suggest you start with doing some elementary tutorials first.<\/p>\n",
